text: Room for all of your toys! Fantastic location in Birch Bay for a storage condo with improvements. Gated and secure complex. Unit has large storage loft that includes a motorized lift for heavy capacity. Work benches and additional lighting. Built out space for bathroom with plumbing access ready to go upon availability. Backyard Buddy auto lift included up to 7, 000 lbs. Super clean and ready for you!

Fantastic opportunity for multi generational living in one of Blaine's core neighborhoods 3 bedroom/2.5 bathroom, efficient, quality built Craftsman features a functional open living, dining, a custom kitchen with huge island & stainless steel appliances. Permitted detached accessory dwelling (DADU) generously sized 2nd floor studio with a full size kitchen & a 3/4 bath large closet. This is the ideal scenario to work or school from home you decide! Detached 2 car garage, fenced back yard, patio, gardens & fruit trees. Excellent walkable location to the downtown restaurants, shopping, the waterfront & the schools...this is the one you've been waiting for. A great property for those looking to live comfortably

Experience world-class views of the San Juan Islands from the front row of Madrona Pointe, arguably the most coveted enclave of Edgemoor. Westerly exposure floods this custom built stunner with sun & creates the most amazing sunsets. Quality built by Moceri & expanded by Echo Point | pure NW high-end craftsmanship. Features are numerous including a chef's kitchen opening to a breathtaking great room, spa inspired primary suite with fireplace, expansive decks, plus a dedicated theater room. Privacy beckons you throughout the shy 3/4 acre lot of winding gardens, decorative trees & lush lawns. Oversized 3-car garage with breezeway & custom wood doors. Explore Clark's Point steps away from your door or stroll down to Fairhaven Village.
Builders and Investors come see this Vacant Land in Blaine, WA. 7, 993 sq. foot residential lot. Corner Lot.

Early 1900s craftsman located in the best part of Historic York Neighborhood! Nelson's Market is just around the corner and Downtown Bellingham is only a few blocks away. Original character abounds including hardwood floors, picture windows, tall ceilings, built in features, trim & loads of charm. Spacious living room with a gas fireplace is cozy and welcoming. Dining area off of the kitchen is filled with natural light. Two spacious bedrooms on the main floor and one upstairs with additional loft space. The large unfinished basement adds ample storage space and an additional half bath. Backyard is fully fenced for your privacy and there's additional alley parking for you and your guests.

This custom-designed single level 2, 487 sqft home epitomizes elegance and functionality, perfectly blending open-concept living with the serenity of nature. Vaulted ceilings amplify the sense of space, drawing attention to a dream kitchen that offers stunning bay views through a picturesque window. With 4 cozy bedrooms and 2 modern bathrooms, it comfortably accommodates guests. The home's crown jewel is its outdoor entertainment area, complete with a hot tub (negotiable), set against the tranquil backdrop of a private greenbelt. Nestled on a generously sized lot, this property promises an unparalleled living experience, where luxury meets the peace of the outdoors. Ideal for those who cherish both sophistication and privacy.

Stunning 4-plex in the heart of Ferndale! This beautiful building is only 5 years old and a great investment. Each unit is a huge 1, 560 sq ft, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms. The layout is fantastic! Each unit is 2 levels. The main level has your kitchen, living room w/natural gas fireplace, powder room and deck. Then you either go upstairs or downstairs, depending on the unit, to your 3 beds, 2 bath, and washer & dryer. A perfect design for quiet nights rest with the separation of bedrooms. Building is fully leased boasting a self managed CAP rate of 5.63%! Look at the rents, there is defiantly room for an increase per unit. Seller currently pays water & sewer but units are separately metered w/another opportunity to make the CAP rate soar!

Estate sale. Welcome to Sealinks, a gated community in Birch Bay. This home built in 2001, is a one owner home, single level & amazing. Clean, neat, bright with excellent sun exposure. 1287 sq. ft, 3 bedroom, 1.75 baths, 2 car garage on a 6035 sq ft. homesite. New Roof, gutters and exterior paint summer of 2023. Hardi siding, with large covered front porch, as well as spacious back deck in parklike setting. Home has natural gas forced air heat, natural gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings in the Great room concept. Enjoy the newer appliance package complete with washer and dryer. This development has front and back gates with access to the heart of Birch Bay including restaurants, beach access, new walking berm and community park. Nice location.

Spectacular views of Bellingham Bay!!! The mature lot lends to a tree house like feel featuring breath taking sunsets. The large living and dining room highlight the incredible views and feature original wood ceilings and large windows. The primary bedroom, with en-suite, is on the main level for ease of access. The lower level has an additional living room space and lots of storage as well as two bedrooms and a full bathroom. Recent upgrades include: high end vinyl plank waterproof flooring in the kitchen and entryway, new carpet in the lower level and primary bedroom, and fresh interior paint. There is level covered parking and room for up to 3 vehicles. You're just minutes to Fairhaven, Boulevard Park, and downtown Bellingham!

Step into luxury & comfort w/this stunning remodeled home nestled on one of the largest corner lots in the area. Boasting 3 bed & 2 bath, this residence offers ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The fully fenced backyard with a patio and shed provides a private oasis for outdoor gatherings and leisure activities. Inside, you'll find a seamless blend of style & functionality, spaciouss living room, family room, and a huge bonus room w/its own patio access. The owner's suite is complete w/large dual closets & an ensuite bath featuring a gorgeous tiled shower, adding a touch of elegance to your daily routine. New roof installed in 2016 and fresh paint throughout. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home

Introducing this charming 3-bed, 1.75-bath home featuring brand-new roof and gutters! With 1609 sq ft, it's impeccably maintained, showcasing mature landscaping, a serene garden area, and an expansive patio. The large country-style kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and stunning granite countertops. Enjoy the inviting open floor plan, ideal for hosting gatherings. Conveniently located near trails, parks, Lake Whatcom, restaurants, schools and shopping.

Welcome to this charming single-level home, a perfect blend of comfort and style spanning 1, 500 square feet. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this residence offers an inviting ambiance and thoughtful design throughout. Home offers newly painted interior walls, new carpet in the primary bedrooms, newly installed gas range and refrigerator, furnace recently serviced, and the air ducts cleaned. With the perfect open floor plan for entertaining and a patio with a view of the mountains, come see this quality home!

3 bedroom / 2 bath Chalet style home with architectural details throughout. Spacious kitchen with newly installed cabinets. Large laundry/mud room. Full size basement and front deck.This home is ideally located and zoned for Small Cottage home business. 40x60 Shop with independent 200 amp meter service, 3 phrase converter with bridge crane. Shop includes office space, upstairs storage room, 3 bay doors and is heated by 115K BTU propane heater. Assessable to Semi-trucks. Has multiple out buildings. Mature landscaping provide privacy from street. The home is exceptionally quiet and sound-deadening, the difference is astonishing.

Fairytale property sitting on 6+ acres adjacent to DNR land for guaranteed privacy & direct private access to Stewart Mtn trail system! This rare, single level, updated, meticulously maintained home offers everything you could want: 3 bedrooms + den, 2 car shop w/ 1/2 bath & a studio! Major recent updates include, roof in 2018, addtl 2 bed septic at shop, high end kitchen remodel, hardwood flrs, heat pump + A/C (home & shop), LED lights throughout, Hardie siding, ext paint & stain, front porch decking + stairs, crawlspace clean out, french drain, 220 in shop, 2 x RV hookups. The list goes on... Thoughtful drought resistant landscape on drip lines, & deer protected garden w/ raised beds & potting/wood shed. Circular driveway! A Must See!

Quiet and private affordable home on corner lot. This home has a single car garage, a single carport and a large high roof RV or boat garage. Nice covered west facing back patio with fully fenced bark yard is ideal for summer bbq's. Lots of storage space. Outbuilding for lawn and garden equipment. This home could use some updating but seller has priced it accordingly.

Come discover the latest 20 lot phase in Hannah Creek by Skeers Construction. An amazing location for outdoor exploration with access to 65+ miles of mountain biking, hiking, and trail running on the adjacent 3000 acre Galbraith Mountain trail system. Whatcom Falls Park is just down the street, and downtown is less than 3 miles away. West facing lot backs to peaceful, wooded greenbelt with creek. Open great room floor plan features main floor primary suite and home office, plus two large upper floor bedrooms. Big windows bring in gorgeous natural light and woodsy views. High tech energy features include heat pump heating and cooling with energy recovery ventilation system, and an efficient hybrid heat pump hot water heater.

Experience the ultimate in tranquil living with this stunning mountain view home nestled in the picturesque Glenhaven Lakes neighborhood. Enjoy exclusive access to amenities including a clubhouse, pool, and serene lake for endless relaxation and recreation. Step onto your spacious deck to soak in breathtaking views of the surrounding peaks, creating the perfect backdrop for entertaining or simply unwinding after a long day. With its idyllic setting and array of amenities, this home offers a lifestyle of comfort and leisure that's truly unmatched.

Welcome to 3118 Firwood Ave in charming Bellingham! This delightful property offers everything you need for comfortable living and more. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and 1, 092 square feet of living space, this cozy abode is perfect for those seeking a much sought after home in Bellingham. Situated on a generous .38-acre lot with a fully fenced yard, you will be all set with your pets and have plenty of gardening space. There is also a sizeable gardening shed and clothes line. The one car garage offers a wall of cupboards and drawers for tools, sports equipment, or seasonal decorations along with a spacious work bench. New roof installed in 2022.

Welcome to your dream home! Introducing our exquisite new 2-story Bluff floorplan featuring 3 beds & 3 baths. Enjoy the spacious upper deck with breathtaking water views and stunning sunsets over Birch Bay. The primary suite is a true haven, boasting a lavish 5-piece ensuite and a huge walk-in closet, providing ample space for all your needs. The lower level boasts a bonus room with fully tiled shower and optional wet bar. Luxury abounds with ceramic tiles, custom hickory-stained cabinets, and high-end appliances in the chef's dream kitchen. Proximity to golf clubs, Semiahmoo, Vancouver BC, and Seattle. Indulge in the epitome of elegance and coastal living. Your perfect oasis awaits.

Located in the historic Sehome Hill neighborhood, this 4bd home offers stunning views of Mt Baker, the Canadian Mts & the city. Renovated with modern amenities & classic charm, the main floor welcomes you with an open layout with a stylish kitchen/dining area, vaulted ceilings, & abundant natural light. A cozy sunroom offers a versatile space for work or relaxation. Upstairs the primary suite awaits with a private balcony, custom-tiled shower & walk in closet. Below a spacious bonus room with a separate entrance provides endless possibilities as a home office, gym, or potential MIL suite. The large deck & sunny fenced yard invite outdoor living. Savor the best of Bellingham living with downtown, the Arboretum, and more just a stroll away.

Lynden Gem! This Lynden home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.25 bathrooms.The generous primary bedroom features a double sink and walk-in closet. Enjoy a finished basement with extra living room/ play room. Situated on a large corner lot, relish the fully fenced backyard, a 2-car garage, a new deck (2023) plus a tool and garden shed. This home offers unique functionality in an ideal location! Close to schools, parks and walking distance to town amenities!

Tremendous investment opportunity located in the heart of Lynden. Nice residential neighborhood, great condition, & solid cap rate of 5.16. You'll be hard pressed to find a better product for your investment portfolio. Newer exterior paint w/low maintenance Hardie Siding. Major refresh in unit B for 2022, new carpeting, interior paint, blinds, led lighting & beautiful LG appliances. Each unit has their own 2 car garage, fully fenced private backyards, and patios. Identical spacious floor plans include 3 large bedrooms, 2 full baths, one 1/2 bath, plus over 1500sqft. Main floor primary w/lg walk-in closets & oversized soaker tub/shower. The second & third bedrooms are upstairs along with the second full bath. Tenant pays all utilities.

Welcome to your new home! Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this charming 3 bedroom, 2.75 bathroom house offers both comfort and style. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the inviting rambler layout, designed for seamless living and entertaining. The spacious living area is perfect for cozy gatherings or relaxing evenings in front of the fireplace. The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage. Retreat to the tranquil primary suite, complete with a private ensuite bathroom and walk- in closet for added convenience. Two additional bedrooms offer flexibility for guests, a home office, or whatever suits your lifestyle. Step outside to discover the fully fenced backyard oasis!

Recently remodeled and upgraded rambler on 1.13 flat acre lot four miles from Bellingham city limits. On a dead-end road that provides a quiet and private location. Level lot provides lots of room for gardens and areas for enlarging existing 900 SF detached garage/shop or other buildings. The many upgrades include Hardi-plank siding, double pane vinyl windows, a 14KW Generac generator, Solar Panels with 30 panels provide practically zero power bills, a new Rainni on-demand water heater. Plus new flooring and kitchen cabinets. The new roof was installed in September, 2023 and old roof was taken down to the rafters with new sheathing, underlayment, GAF Silver Pledge 50 year limited warranty and new ridge vents. VACANT GO SHOW.

Experience Single Level Luxury Living in one of Bellingham's Vibrant Neighborhoods. This home features 3 Bedrooms, 1.75 Bathrooms, and a seamlessly designed Great Room that combines Open Living and Dining Areas with a tremendous amount of Natural Light. The Chef's Kitchen boasts Upgraded Cabinetry and Appliances, while the High Ceilings and Vaulted Great Room enhance the spacious feel. The Large Primary Bedroom features a Beautiful En Suite and Spacious Closet. Outside, enjoy a low-maintenance Fully Fenced Backyard with a Large Covered Patio. Conveniently located near Major Amenities, this residence is the perfect balance of Comfort and Style.

Inviting investors and visionaries! This property is an investor's delight, offering a unique opportunity to transform a home affected by a flood. Stripped down to the studs in most places, this blank canvas awaits someone with the vision to bring it back to life. Priced to sell! Seize the chance to reimagine and rebuild your dream investment awaits!

Welcome to Ferndale Estates, where affordability meets comfort! Delightful 3 bed / 2 bath home offers serene surroundings & park amenities. Experience a spacious main living area, boasting vaulted ceilings w/ an open floor plan seamlessly connecting the living room, dining room & fully equipped kitchen. With 3 generously sized bedrooms, including a primary bedroom w/ ensuite. Recent updates include: luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, baseboard trim, new drywall, fresh interior paint, ceiling fan, new primary bathroom , 2nd bathroom new vanity & toilet, 2019 kitchen appliances & water heater. Newer roof ~ 6 yrs old. Community park, basketball hoop & on-site management. Minutes to main street Ferndale, Only 15 mins to Bellingham!

Beautifully updated home, nestled in the heart of Bellingham, in a welcoming 55+ community. The home offers a warm & inviting living space, spacious kitchen, newer appliances, fresh interior paint, updated double pane windows, laminate flooring & an upgraded ductless heat pump for your heating & cooling needs. Your new home comes with a very large designated covered parking space. Outside you will find a good sized shed for storage and an expansive covered deck, including a wheel chair ramp for easy access. As part of the 55+ park, you'll have access to a range of amenities, including a clubhouse and community events. The location is situated near local shops, restaurants, medical facilities, easy I-5 access & various recreational options.

This home, the Alder plan, is a 1527 SF, 2BR, 2.25BA, 2-car garage home w/a spacious great room, open kitchen w/eating bar, quartz countertops, white cabinet package w/soft-close doors & drawers, water-resistant planked flooring, nine-foot ceilings on the main, primary suite w/luxury bath, & convenient upper floor laundry. These all-electric homes include energy-efficient mini-split heat & A/C units, fireplaces, & 80-gallon hybrid heat pump water heaters, plus an energy-efficient insulation package w/soundproofing. The Alpengrove neighborhood has an appealing modern aesthetic w/inviting front porches, both private & shared outdoor spaces, plus quick, convenient access to I-5 & all that Bellingham has to offer.

Come see this fantastic home walking distance to Whatcom Falls, in a cul de sac, with a fantastic floor plan and a huge backyard! This home has it all! This house features the primary bedroom on the main level, and additional bedroom with a full bath across the hall in the front of the house on the main level, and a third large bedroom upstairs with a walk in closet and own full bath. Fully fenced backyard is large enough for your biggest dogs AND for all your gardening. Family room is great sized with gas fireplace. Enjoy the peacefulness of a quiet road, the ability to walk to Sunday morning donuts at Lafeens, or lunch at Da Vinci's. Must see this fantastic Bellingham gem!

This well cared-for '08 Breckenridge Park Model & gazebo comfortably sleeps 7 adults. Vaulted ceilings, electric fireplace & full size appliances are just some of the features that make it feel like home. Beautiful, gated covered deck w/ skylights provides for year-round enjoyment of the outdoors. The thoughtfully designed lot is fully fenced & backs up to greenbelt offering privacy & is just steps from Gorge Trail. There's also a covered BBQ area & wood shed. The Glen at Maple Falls is just 15-minutes from the base of Mt. Baker & Silver Lake. Amenities include Nooksack River access, two pools, tennis & basketball courts, playgrounds, parks, trails, disc golf, 24/7 security & more. No rentals. Occupancy is limited to 120 days/year.

Turnkey One-Level Home that Lives Large on Barkley Hill! Vaulted Ceilings. Cherrywood Hardwood Floors. Sunny & Bright! East/West All Day Sunlight! 3 Bedrooms, 2-Full Baths, with Soaking Tub in Primary Bedroom. Approximately 1, 800 s.f. on a 12K+ Lot. New Roof in February 2024. Hardi-Plank Siding. Air Conditioning! Gas Heat, Tankless H20, Large Fenced Corner Lot! Over-sized 2-Car Garage. Fenced Backyard, Patio & Gazebo. Working Hot Tub!

Cute little cottage style 2 bedroom, 1 bath home. Quiet location, and just a short walk to the thriving downtown corridor, awesome restaurants, Starbucks, and Blaine's ever improving waterfront, and marina. Zoning is SF2 which may allow for further development. This zoning can accommodate both a single family home and an ADU. Great for MIL, rental, etc. Terrific investment with upside potential. New roof & exterior paint in 2022. Brand new stove, newer washer/dryer, & laminate flooring! All will enjoy the huge front yard plus alley access for off street parking. Gas Heat (free standing fireplace) and hot water. Updated double pane windows throughout. Come and take a look today!

Custom-designed home featuring stunning pond & Mt. Baker views. Enjoy a one-level living design w/ spacious living room, vaulted ceilings & built-in storage. Skylights & large southern-facing windows bathe the interior in natural light. Two main-level suites w/ adjoining baths, including a massive walk-in closet & dedicated office space. The large partially finished basement provides versatile living options with separate access, ideal for multigenerational living or as a future income producing rental space. Each floor features expansive decks for relaxation. Updates include siding/paint, newer furnace, and a whole-house dehumidifier. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood with walkable trails and conveniently close to the new High School.

Step into your dream home! Nestled in one of Bellingham's premier neighborhoods, this captivating 4bd/2.25ba abode beckons you. Picture-perfect open-concept living spills onto a deck, treating you to breathtaking territorial vistas. Immerse yourself in the vibrant Barkley Village scene just a short walk away. With downtown, Lake Whatcom, and endless trails within reach, adventure awaits at every turn. Don't just imagine your ideal lifestylelive it in this inviting haven!

Well cared for '82 Travel Eze park model at The Glen at Maple Falls. Pie shaped lot backs up to greenbelt. Very spacious inside of unit. Large primary bedroom in back. Large, covered deck for entertaining. Shed stays nice and dry. This is a must see in highly sought after Division 4. Located minutes away to Mt. Baker for skiing in the winter or hiking in the summer. The Glen has 2 pools, (1 open year-round) hot tub, sauna, 2 clubhouses, tennis courts, disc golf course, bike pump track, river access, trails, laundry facilities, restroom and shower facilities, library, 24/7 security, and so much more. Zoned rec for 120 days use per year. This is a must see.

Here is your slice of natural paradise amidst pristine forest land. Discover the perfect canvas for your dream home on an expansive 70+ acres. With Baker views from the cleared 1-acre build site, this offers a rare opportunity to create a legacy property in a serene & secluded environment. Fully serviced & ready to build w/ 4-bed septic installed in 2021, power on-site & 3 connected water shares w/ add'l shares available. Approved site plan for home + detached garage w/ ADU. Brand new 24'x48' shop incl. 100 amp panel, metal roof, 10' door + rear man door. Shipping container w/ 40 amp panel. Includes mineral rights w/ exploratory natural gas well. 20-acre exemption to subdivide may be possible. Zoned forestry w/ low property taxes.

Step into this meticulously maintained single-level charmer & prepare to relax, all the work has been done for you! Showcasing a fully remodeled kitchen featuring new cabinets, quartz counters, and stainless steel appliances - make your culinary dreams come true. A refreshed bathroom is nestled between two roomy bedrooms, bathed in natural light. With fresh interior paint, a newer roof, and a newer mini-split system, comfort and style await. Embrace indoor-outdoor living w/a spacious & sunny fenced backyard and covered patio for relaxation. A roomy garage is perfect for vehicles or outdoor gear storage. Enjoy exclusive access to Glenhaven Lakes featuring a clubhouse, seasonal pool, tennis court, parks, playground and 2 lakes.

Well maintained home in Bay Ridge Estates nestled at the end of a quiet street! This 3-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom residence features a thoughtfully designed open floor plan flooded with natural light. This home features gas fireplace, new laminate flooring, tastefully updated bathrooms, walk-in closets in every bedroom & more. Welcoming front deck, perfect for enjoying the serene surroundings. Situated on a level, sunny lot with partially fenced backyard, cherry tree & garden shed! Great location, Birch Bay's stunning beaches and amenities are just a short stroll away, every day feels like a getaway in paradise.

Welcome to your cozy retreat in Everson! This delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom bungalow boasts a flood-free history and has undergone a recent makeover. Revel in the fresh paint adorning both the interior and exterior, along with upgraded fiber cement siding, a brand-new ductless HVAC system for enhanced climate control, a sturdy new roof, and meticulously restored landscaping. A convenient attached garage offers space for parking or tinkering. Outside, the fully fenced backyard features a generous covered area, perfect for a kennel, chicken coop, or additional storage. Enjoy the charm and functionality of this inviting home!

PNW Lifestyle! This beautifully finished 2, 784 sf home sits above Lake Whatcom w/in an oasis of natures beauty & privacy. Throw open the double french doors for connected deck living which easily transitions into the light-filled open concept living room. 4 beds, 2.5 baths, plus a family room & office. Primary suite on main floor w/vaulted ceilings & large walk-in closet. A/C, tankless water heater, granite counters, gas fireplace, wet bar & easy maintenance yard lends to a seamless life here. Flat driveway leads to oversized garage, room for 6 cars. Located in highly desired Gate 2, take the short path to AM/PM beach (revered as the best on Lake Whatcom) to paddleboard, kayak, swim or simply sit beachside. Close to the golf course & pool.

Presale offer! The Cypress, a 2, 690 sq ft, 3 bed/2.25 bath home, available at a reasonable price. Located in Woodberry, a secure, gated community, it's 25 mins from Costco & 45 mins from Vancouver, BC. Features include office/dining area, loft, 9ft ceilings, mini split & AC. High-quality flooring, soft-close cabinets, gas fireplace & stove, spacious walk-in closets. Tranquil setting with ample space between houses, surrounded by trees. Luxury amenities at Semiahmoo Resort. Site registration in place. Don't miss this opportunity for a home in a serene locale. Pick color scheme & upgrades now!

What you've been waiting for! Meticulously maintained single story home with the ideal layout. Situated within walking distance of Lookout Mtn Nature Preserve, it's nestled on a tranquil private road, w/ updated landscaping, fenced backyard, and a newer roof for peace of mind. Inside, you'll discover a primary bedroom complete with an en-suite bath & walk-in closet, alongside 2 additional bedrooms and a 2nd bath. The heart of the home is the open concept kitchen with granite countertops, living, and dining area, designed for seamless entertaining and everyday living. With access to all Sudden Valley amenities such as the marina, 18-hole championship golf course, tennis courts, gym, seasonal pool, and much more - this checks all the boxes.

Discover your next home, nestled near the vibrant heartbeat of Western Washington University and the historic charm of the Fairhaven community. This inviting 5-bedroom, 3 bath home promises more than just four walls; it offers a lifestyle. Youre close to all that Bellingham has to offer: shopping, parks, artisanal delights and eateries, and if youre so inclined - embracing an outdoor life! And even if youre more the inside type - enjoy the Pacific Northwest's natural beauty, all right at your doorstep. Curious to explore? Your new adventure awaits at 1024 34th St. All new paint - in and out - new countertops in kitchen, all systems recently checked - and more! Experience the essence of Bellingham living schedule your tour today!

Light & Bright 2 bedroom Bellingham Condo! Lovely open-concept floorplan with a gas fireplace in living room, sunny dining area with deck access, and the fresh white kitchen with breakfast bar and plenty of counter/cabinet space. 2 spacious bedrooms, both with access to the deck with green belt & golf course peek-a-boo views, including a primary suite with walk-in closet and private full bath. Modern LVP flooring, in-unit laundry room, ample natural light throughout, 1 included reserved parking space, and more! Located near parks, golfing, shops, restaurants, I-5 and Bellingham Bay. Don't miss out on this one!

Charming county setting for this one level custom-built home, only 20 minutes to Bellingham or Lynden. Come create your own happy memories here! Enjoy the gourmet kitchen w/higher end SS appliances, Silestone countertops, custom cherry cabinets & access to the back patio. Watch the birds while relaxing by the double-sided fireplace in the living room w/vaulted ceilings or the dining room through large picture windows. An extra-large office is just off the entry/could be 3rd bedroom. The luxurious primary bedroom is large enough for a sitting area, has a private patio, a walk-in closet, dual basins, jetted soaker tub & shower. 2 mini splits keep you cool in the summer. The heated garage is lined w/built-in cabinets. Many mature fruit trees!

Your dream coastal getaway awaits! Take in awe-inspiring views of majestic Lummi Bay & Mt. Baker all from your private, low bank, waterfront oasis with 59' of beachfront. Your thoughtfully designed living space includes soaring ceilings, AC, and an expansive garage with bonus work area. Transition seamlessly from indoor to outdoor living with direct access from your primary bedroom or living room to discover an outdoor entertainer's dream, complete with dining table for 10, bistro lights, and a beautiful hot tub. Sip coffee as you watch the sun rise over the bay and enjoy a glass of wine as you catch sunsets to the west from your second floor balcony. Enjoy community amenities such as the pool, golf course, and a marina. This is the one!
nearby_schools: Ferndale School District, Lummi High School, Lummi Elementary School

text: BIRCHWOOD MID-CENTURY RAMBLER features 2 BR's + 1 updated bath, sited at the front of a MASSIVE .66 acre lot w/giant old growth fir! New roof in 2022, oak floors, galley kitchen w/handmade cabinets, laundry room with included washer/dryer + utility sink. Former garage converted to shop/studio space w/loft sleeping area, office, play room or ?? Entertain in the covered gazebo & take advantage of multiple outbuildings for storage. Conveniently across the street from Birchwood Park, which connects to Squalicum Creek Park, its vast amenities & space. This gorgeous, expansive lot is 80' wide 360' deep. Build your dream house + shop in back & keep the existing house as an ADU.
